            <button id="consent-button">I Agree</button>
        </div>
    </div>


<div class="home-page-background">
    <div class="content">
        <div class="home-info">
            <p><b>Explore the Capabilities of Generative Artificial Intelligence </b></p>
            <p>This demonstration provides a glimpse into the versatility and efficiency of integrating cutting-edge technology to support NATO’s Joint Analysis & Lessons Learned Centre, designed specifically to cater to its internal users’ and stakeholders' needs.</p>
            
